    "142 Madden et al. [16] 2023 Health \"AI hallucination\" occurs when ChatGPT generates false information, also called \"delusions.\"",
    "143 Komorowski [169] 2023 Health \"AI hallucination\" refers to the phenomenon where ChatGPT has the ability to confidently produce answers that appear believable but may be incorrect or nonsensical.",
    "144 Sallam [170] 2023 Health/ Academia \"AI hallucination\" refers to concerns arising from possible bias in ChatGPT's training datasets, limiting its capabilities and potentially causing factual inaccuracies that, surprisingly, seem scientifically plausible.",
